title: "09: Explosives in Cyberspace"
---

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(mistlecode)

dt <- readLines("input.txt")
```
:::





## Part 1





::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
markers <-
  dt |>
  stringr::str_extract_all("\\(\\d+x\\d+\\)") |>
  unlist() |>
  stringr::str_remove_all("\\(|\\)") |>
  stringr::str_split_fixed("x", 2) |>
  as.integer() |>
  matrix(ncol = 2)

dt |>
  stringr::str_replace_all("(\\(\\d+x\\d+\\))", "_")
```
